feat(lever-2a): restartScanFromForeground entry for FGS-owned scan re-register

Provides MobBleNative.restartScanFromForeground() so the meshx_mobile_app
foreground service can rebind an active scan to the foreground-app context
after startForeground. Empirically did not change locked-receive on T577U
(scan stayed unfiltered, Samsung still suspended on screen-off), but the
entry point is the right shape for the next experiment.

